## Questions for Yauhen before drafting

1. **Link the live pub or not?** — Dubliners Strasbourg site is real; if we link it, we're driving traffic to a client. Fine, or anonymize as "an Irish pub in Strasbourg"?
2. **How technical should I go?** — I have it spined as build-log with 2 short code snippets. Tighter (no code, all narrative) or looser (more code)?
3. **Anti-template-slop story strength** — the "I refused the shamrock" beat is the strongest narrative thread. Want me to lead with it, or keep it as section 5?
